body:
✈️ my baby’s fly like a jet stream ✈️

AUCKLAND SIGN ++ COSTUME REVEAL!!

(A8 - P - 21-22)

Believe it or not but I actually made this costume before Taylor pointed at my CIWYW themed sign!! But yes this is my Auckland outfit! Is it weird I’m super excited to walk around with little pictures of joe on my clothes?? Anyway I’m super excited to be meeting all my kiwi Internet friends at the show!! It will sadly be my last show this tour but I am so overwhelmingly greatful to be able to experience this tour!! To everyone who couldn’t make it, don’t lose hope because one day it’ll happen for you!! Love you guys && can’t wait to see you at the shows!!
